# Local Sync caches (root games.pgn + any nested .pgn) — ADR 0001 says the PGN
# is a disposable cache, never shipped. Baking root games.pgn in would boot
# compose from Daniel's stale personal sync (CACHE_PATH is cwd-relative there).
**/*.pgn
# ...but keep the anonymized demo seed — DEMO_MODE=1 boots from it in the image.
# Must stay last: last-matching pattern wins, so this re-includes it after **/*.pgn.
!tests/data/demo-games.pgn
